<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>新建Wiki词条 - OpenClaw Community</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-book text-info"></i> 新建Wiki词条</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="alert alert-info">
              <i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i> 词条提交后需要管理员审核才会显示
            </div>
            <form action="/wiki" method="POST">
              <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">词条名称 *</label>
                <input type="text" name="title" class="form-control" placeholder="如：OpenClaw, AI Agent, Prompt Engineering" required>
              </div>

              <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">URL标识 *</label>
                <input type="text" name="slug" class="form-control" placeholder="如：openclaw, ai-agent（仅支持英文、数字、连字符）" required>
                <div class="form-text">用于URL访问，如 /wiki/openclaw</div>
              </div>

              <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">分类 *</label>
                <select name="category" class="form-select" required>
                  <option value="">选择分类</option>
                  <option value="concept">基础概念</option>
                  <option value="tool">工具/平台</option>
                  <option value="technique">技术方法</option>
                  <option value="case">案例实践</option>
                  <option value="other">其他</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">词条内容 * (支持Markdown)</label>
                <textarea name="content" class="form-control" rows="15" placeholder="# 词条标题

## 简介
简要介绍这个名词...

## 详细说明
详细内容...

## 相关链接
- [链接1](url)
- [链接2](url)" required></textarea>
              </div>

              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                <a href="/wiki" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">取消</a>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info text-white">
                  <i class="bi bi-check-lg"></i> 提交审核
                </button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
